Description:
We Happy Few - the history of the gang is not too pleasant, but the brave guys trying to escape from the city of Wellington Wells from the joyful idiocy of local life. You must merge with the residents of a drug-injected retrofuturistic city in an alternative England of the 1960s - they do not like people who refuse to live according to its insane rules. Disclose the dark history of the city, playing the intertwining stories of three quiet rebels, the inhabitants of Wellington Wells. Each of them manifests its strengths and weaknesses, looking at its past, preparing for the future and participating in actions that violate the tranquility of an artificially enthusiastic society
